  <h1>Why Your FastBots Chatbot Gives Wrong Answers — And How to Fix It</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">FastBots' homepage promises a chatbot that "always has the right answer." If yours does not, the problem is almost certainly in one of three places — none of which require you to abandon the platform.</p>

  <div class="metadata-box">
