    <p><strong>Source reliability labels:</strong> <span class="rel-label verified">Verified</span> = independently verifiable from primary sources (e.g., NVIDIA technical blog, IBM developer docs). <span class="rel-label vendor">Vendor Claim</span> = from FastBots' own marketing or documentation. <span class="rel-label third-party">Third-Party Reported</span> = from independent industry sources or reviewers. <span class="rel-label self-reported">Self-Reported</span> = from user-generated review platforms. <span class="rel-label unverified">Unverified</span> = could not be confirmed at time of writing.</p>
